Step by step

  • Identify RED, NIR, and fmask layers using list.file()

    • list.files(dir, pattern = glob2rx('*fmask*.tif'), full.names = TRUE)
  • (Calculate NDVI -> apply cloud mask) * 2
  • Crop to intersecting extent
    • intersect()

  • Substract the two layers

  • No need to stack
